uk.ac.open.kmi.iserve.sal.manager

Interface NfpManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    iServeComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NfpManagerSparql

    public interface NfpManager
extends iServeComponent
    Interface that defines the operations a NFP Manager should offer If other implementations backed by different types of storage systems are needed we should update this.
    Author:
    Carlos Pedrinaci (KMi - The Open University), Luca Panziera (KMi - The Open University)
